<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 10pt; TEXT-ALIGN: center; mso-line-height-alt: 9.45pt; mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto" align=center><B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'">Efficacy of neurofeedback treatment in ADHD: The effects on inattention, impulsivity and hyperactivity: <BR>A meta-analysis.</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 7pt; COLOR: black; FONT-FAMILY: 'Arial','sans-serif'; mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'"><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P></FONT></SPAN>
